MTF,<br><br>
The boys of that group have been pounding the crap out of my back forty.  I hear the thunder almost every night now that they are warming up for the GULF War Games.<br><br>
Sweet music to sleep by.  When you feel the ground trembling a bit it brings back memories.<br><br>
DZ says it would drive him crazy.  Come to think of it that should be no effect at all.<br><br>
Fort Hood Robert Gray is BIIIGGGG Place.  Have you seen that much fire power and armor since VN?  Last time on post two weeks ago.<br><br>
I knew you would get them cranked up.  One area I was in had aframed PIC of an M-60, Apache and the new Commanche on the wall.  Must like that shoot-em-up stuuff.  HA!<br><br>
Now that you have them all stirred up I'll have to listen to the noise.  Sweet.
